			     DNSSEC-Tools
			Is your domain secure?

This directory contains files that provide DNSSEC validation to the sendmail
Mail Tranfer Agent.

[1]
The spfmilter-0.97_dnssec_patch.txt file contains a patch to spfmilter-0.97
that provides DNSSEC validation.  It uses the API from libspf2 with the
dnssec_patch applied (see ../libspf2/README).

[2]
The spfmilter-dnssec-howto.txt file contains instructions for adding
DNSSEC validation to spfmilter.

[3]
The sendmail-8.14.6_dnssec_patch.txt file contains a patch to sendmail-8.14.6
that provides DNSSEC validation for DNS queries within the sendmail Mail
Transfer Agent (MTA).

[4]
The sendmail-dnssec-howto.txt file contains instructions for adding
DNSSEC validation to the sendmail MTA.

